```

Returns the claimed occupied cells for an entity as positions.

#### `getReservedCells(entity)`

```typescript
getReservedCells(entity: EntityId): Position[]
```

Returns the claimed reserved cells for an entity as positions.

#### `getMetrics()`

```typescript
